

how to test 
1. Start The Broker
cd C:\custom_secure_mqtt_broker\secure-mqtt-broker
.\start_broker.bat
Leave this window open. 

2. Open A Second PowerShell Window
Run the dashboard subscriber:
mosquitto_sub -h localhost -p 1884 -u dashboard -P 906271 -t sensors/#   Leave it waiting.

3. Open A Third PowerShell Window
Publish as the authorized sensor:
mosquitto_pub -h localhost -p 1884 -u temperature_sensor -P 906271 -t sensors/temperature -m "25.6"
In the subscriber window, you should see:
25.6

4. Test Unauthorized User
Try attacker:
mosquitto_pub -h localhost -p 1884 -u attacker -P 906271 -t sensors/temperature -m "hacked"

The dashboard should not receive hacked.

5. Test Wrong Topic
Try the temperature sensor on a topic it is not allowed to publish to:
mosquitto_pub -h localhost -p 1884 -u temperature_sensor -P 906271 -t sensors/humidity -m "60"
The dashboard should not receive 60.